Package files

Class FileSet

java.lang.Object
files.FileSet
Direct Known Subclasses:
TestSet, TrainSet
public class FileSet
extends java.lang.Object
Receives the file and decomposes them line by line, sending it to the correct place. It can receive a train set or a test set.
